Teaching a K POP in Korea . . . A dream come true !! Thinking back on one of the best experiences of my career and my life. Who would have thought I would one day go to Asia and teach a Zumba class. Thank you @zumba.rani @world.zumba.festival for the opportunity. Forever grateful 💙💙💙 And it was really an honor to share the stage with the amazing South Korea team and the other international presenters. It was truly a humbling experience and I learned ALOT from all of them. My biggest take away was that a Zumba class is so much more than a class … it’s an experience 👏✨ Thank you for the memories ❤️ I hope to have the opportunity to come back again soon. Kamsahamnida. Much Z LOVE ❤️‍🔥❣️🫰

EAST COAST 🚨🚨🚨 Get ready to dance into the New Year with our electrifying Zumba class on January 7th, 2024 at 1 PM with @izzycervantes_ from New Mexico, & Giovanna! Join us for a fitness fiesta that will set the tone for an energetic and vibrant year ahead. Whether you’re a seasoned Zumba enthusiast or a first-timer, this event promises to be an unforgettable celebration of music, movement, and pure joy. Izzy will also be having a ZIN Jam Session for all ZIN members right before the masterclass. 

🌟 Date: January 7th, 2024
🕓 Time: 1 PM - 2:30 PM
📍 Location: BQE Fitness- 26-50 Brooklyn Queens Expwy W, Woodside NY 11377
Special Guests: @astriddmichelle @drea124 @kristinacasserole @natlie21 @zinjoelny 

🏆 VIP entry includes:
Meet & Greet and picture with the instructors.
Early access to the event. 
Professional photography before and during the class.
Front row spots.
Gift bag.
🚗 FREE PARKING IS AVAILABLE! 
🎟️Tickets at the door space permitting will be $40 for general admission so get them in advance instead! 
GXVNA MEMBERS GET 30% OFF OF THEIR TICKET!

Incredulously grateful to experience another New Years Eve. Thank you God for the blessings, the hardships, and  everything in between. To my family and friends - I love you all. One of my favorite quotes from Lewis Carroll reads, “It’s no use going back to yesterday, I was a different person then.” I can’t think of a more perfect phrase as I go into the new year with new confidence, wisdom, and courage. 

Thank you 2023 - it was great.

2024… I’m ready. #HNY

Guess who came to NYC and is teaching a Zumba class here tomorrow!? @izzycervantes_ just landed 🛬 and of course the first thing we did was dance 😂💃. We still have some space left for tomorrow’s masterclass at @bqefitness at 1 PM in Queens, NY & Izzy has a Jam session at 9 AM right before the class! Come out and dance with us at the first Zumba event of 2024! If you’re not in NYC you can join us virtually! Sign up on www.gxvna.com.
